attributes.title: Great app
attributes.review: This is my favorite app. It's solved all my problems. My phone is slower than ever and the random glitching since downloading this app is very exciting. I especially love when my phone crashes and I am reminded to take time away from electronics. All that pesky extra storage I had is gone, what a relief. My fridge is very warm and the aliens in my backyard are starting to get testy but those are probably unrelated. Overall I rate the app a 10/10
